{"tid":943122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV男優朝8晚11生活　清水健：為工作8年無休每天貢獻精力","createTime":"2018-12-16T10:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T10:30:42.000Z","uid":86587,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4700c4ea4e26b433e4a308d20a44a98465f45a00","tid":943122,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2090000/2093224/avman_thumb_20180613_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2090000%2F2093224%2Favman_thumb_20180613_ch_1024.jpg&h=c25ee50f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 清水健現時已為一線AV男優，每周的收入最高可達280萬日圓（約20萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\nAV男優的工作看似令人羨慕，他們的收入、生活又是如何？日本著名AV男優、出道20年的38歲清水健曾自言能夠於90分鐘內射精15次，至今拍攝過的作品逾8,000部，有指他初出道時，首部片酬只有1.5萬日圓（約1,100港元）；現時已為一線男優的清水健，每周的收入最高可達280萬日圓（約20萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n今年初，清水健被爆出買Audi跑車時直接付現金，令人驚訝；其經理人及後解釋，AV男優無法申請信用卡或貸款，清水健才要以現金買車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2090000/2093224/shimikan_07_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2090000%2F2093224%2Fshimikan_07_1024.JPG&h=14807036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 清水健被爆出曾直接付現金買Audi跑車。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時日本男優數目約70名，但女優數目則逾萬人。曾有AV男優在日本電視節目上表示，月入平均約20萬至50萬日圓（約1.4萬至3.6萬港元），達「封面級」水平的男優月入可高達100萬日圓（約7.1萬港元）。另一AV男優、39歲鈴木一徹曾透露2004年初入行時，擔任AV配角，只是負責射精，片酬僅有5,000日元（約360港元），但主角則有5萬日元（約3,600港元)，待遇可相差10倍。<br />\n<br />\n清水健早年接受過日本媒體訪問，公開他的日常生活。外形健碩的他，在忙於拍攝AV的同時，每天仍要定時食補充品、勤練肌肉，以維持美好身段。<br />\n<br />\n【早上】<br />\n<br />\n8時：起床吃早餐，喝寶礦力、維他命B、運動補充品BCAA，邊看電視邊進行肌肉訓練。訓練後再吃納豆、番茄、香蕉、乳酪、健胃整腸藥等<br />\n <br />\n9、10時：出門赴拍攝現場，到場後準備拍攝事宜，如剪指甲<br />\n <br />\n11時：開始拍攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2090000/2093224/shimikan_04_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2090000%2F2093224%2Fshimikan_04_1024.JPG&h=a94a1cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 清水健會於早餐時間攝取維他命及補充品。<br />\n<br />\n【下午】<br />\n<br />\n12時：拍攝完畢，服用補充品精胺酸（L-Arginine）、鋅粉<br />\n <br />\n13時：前往健身房做肌肉訓練<br />\n <br />\n16時：開始第二場拍攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2090000/2093224/shimikan_05_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2090000%2F2093224%2Fshimikan_05_1024.JPG&h=74dcc57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 清水健會利用拍攝空檔操肌。<br />\n<br />\n【晚上】<br />\n<br />\n19時：應邀出席商業活動<br />\n <br />\n23時：工作結束回家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2090000/2093224/shimikan_06_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2090000%2F2093224%2Fshimikan_06_1024.JPG&h=c916a9b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 清水健晚上會出席商業活動。<br />\n<br />\n清水健說過：「曾為了工作7、8年都沒有休假，每天不停的貢獻自己的精力。」他又公開了幾個貼士，有助提升床上表現，包括：勤運動，訓練自己的肌肉；每天早睡早起，滴酒不沾，養成健康生活；每天自慰兩次，讓身體記着這種感覺，若不常常射精身體就退化。"},{"pid":"56b87bb187e1a803740fb70cb1dc1079c3b6037a","tid":943122,"uid":130303,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:14:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每天自慰兩次，讓身體記着這種感覺，若不常常射精身體就退化。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a51f1dcc3e10827a6d769476d04b88d06a2dbd6","tid":943122,"uid":198165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁竹口日日都要練先得"},{"pid":"a861e27b81203c8d1e64c7d2ff6baadef7372be7","tid":943122,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56b87bb187e1a803740fb70cb1dc1079c3b6037a","tid":943122,"uid":130303,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:14:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每天自慰兩次，讓身體記着這種感覺，若不常常射精身體就退化。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:25:52.000Z","msg":"認真，自從運動多左，精力真係旺盛左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f357d512448024195b3c651b40f6301aa65d0dbd","tid":943122,"uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"想知佢靠睇咩打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個女優都扑過"},{"pid":"b8c561adb3266e44b21af3264c4d02ad0cced99c","tid":943122,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:26:13.000Z","msg":"粒丸會乾"},{"pid":"c96c37a70615119b6e8d3928555b250da71c7543","tid":943122,"uid":197857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"每日2次 仲有拍野時都射到唔稀既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講唔出句 其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}